title: Indian Asian Grocers
description: Indian and Asian grocery store on the main road of Kangaroo Flat, coming into Bendigo. Everything in the store is vegetarian and many things are vegan. Has breads, packaged snacks, instant meals, frozen foods (like samosas, vegie patties, tikkas, dosa), bulk spices, bulk lentils. bulk grains, Indian sauces. The owner will assist you in finding what's vegan. EFTPOS available, but $10 minimum.
